{"tid":915881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實基哥只要搶到兩至三成票已經足以拖死李卓人 基迷加油呀","createTime":"2018-11-25T09:51:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T12:49:46.000Z","uid":92376,"like":26,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"32f9d61ce2f7144fb139ab40ef616adb58565012","tid":915881,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T09:51:45.000Z","msg":"香港人唔要假民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc9865c6b9d7ba6dd17ea4302d641c8353099e63","tid":915881,"uid":92376,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T09:54:54.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】立法會九西補選投票仍然進行中。前民協元老馮檢基下午約2時半在何文田會見傳媒。他指早上天雨期間到過6、7間酒樓，街坊對他反應正面，不少人都願意和他打招呼、握手，甚至請求合照，令他感到自己的支持度正在上升。<br />\n<br />\n馮檢基亦指出，早上至中午時候的投票率，都較今年3月補選同期上升，他認為數據反映自己的參選，可以令一些年輕選民不用再「含淚」投票或投白票，而投票給他；同時他是唯一在九龍西打拼40年，而且有成績可見的候選人。<br />\n<br />\n被問及若勝選後會否與建制派合作，馮檢基強調民主不可讓步，但民生問題上可以一起逼使特首林鄭月娥做事。至於若落敗後會否再參選，他只表示民主社會下，任何人都應該可以參選，若非建制派一方面繼續稱自己民主，另一方面卻堅持協商欽點、反民主，他仍會考慮參選。<br />\n<br />\n是次補選共有5名候選人，分別為1號伍迪希、2號曾麗文、3號李卓人、4號馮檢基、5號陳凱欣。近49萬名九龍西已登記選民，可於晚上10時半前，到指定投票站投票。<br />\n<br />\n基哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5710af8cef3d36dc95a89aec8c7cd8c14e64c5","tid":915881,"uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T09:57:40.000Z","msg":"陳國強批民主派霸權　不忿馮檢基被欺凌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eac8915c22779286964d23c8b39ad7d69061ef4","tid":915881,"uid":193011,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T10:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cbe6946e083c9e05aefd1dc15f6c4e7e3d1ab3a","tid":915881,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T10:04:40.000Z","msg":"基哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7b1bed664a7fdf3d51036ce6384d0caa387dc6","tid":915881,"uid":192409,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T10:06:58.000Z","msg":"馮檢基原來變左本土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61bb422ef1315cff6f903e50cdd77edab299ce84","tid":915881,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T11:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea5090069f5c3466de71d036678dc89442701310","tid":915881,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T11:49:01.000Z","msg":"GoGoGo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0b7a43ffddb87a381c28fc6b8130279b87bc12","tid":915881,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7a7b1bed664a7fdf3d51036ce6384d0caa387dc6","tid":915881,"uid":192409,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T10:06:58.000Z","msg":"馮檢基原來變左本土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T11:52:58.000Z","msg":"佢只係中間派<br />\n請不要誤導選民，謝謝"},{"pid":"57a9bc4218bd287b6545b964e86b4f00d7788dc8","tid":915881,"uid":137711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T11:53:59.000Z","msg":"你唔係南區㗎咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c00a72df147c7f91decc85aef60a2496673b676","tid":915881,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57a9bc4218bd287b6545b964e86b4f00d7788dc8","tid":915881,"uid":137711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy